data.description: MULTIPLE OFFERS RECEIVED - OFFER DEADLINE MONDAY 4/8 @ 10AM. SELLER RESERVES RIGHT TO ACCEPT OFFER AT ANYTIME Welcome to this exquisite end unit townhome boasting three levels of spacious living with hardwood floors and new carpeting throughout. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances and a sizable island, ideal for entertaining in the open floor concept. Retreat to the primary suite with its walk-in closet and ensuite bathroom, while two additional bedrooms and three and a half bathrooms provide ample space for family and guests. With a two-car garage, large deck, and fenced yard overlooking wooded views, outdoor living is a dream. Enjoy community amenities such as a pool, fitness center, trails, and playgrounds, all in a great neighborhood. Conveniently located near Fort Meade, DC, Baltimore, and major highways, this home offers both luxury and convenience. Don't miss the chance to make it yours! Schedule a showing today.
